I2C Interface:

--------------------------------------------------
software stop
  0x00

--------------------------------------------------
pause
  0x01

--------------------------------------------------
set controller sensor channel
  0x02

--------------------------------------------------
set controller motor channel
  0x03

--------------------------------------------------
set controller P
  0x04

--------------------------------------------------
set controller I
  0x05

--------------------------------------------------
set controller D
  0x06

--------------------------------------------------
set controller target
  0x07
